ferentes tipos (heterogéneos)</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">1.5. Clases</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">1.6. Variables</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">1.7. Funciones</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\nReferencias:\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Google Java Style\" href=\"http://google-styleguide.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/javaguide.html\" target=\"_blank\">Google Java Style</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Training - Android Developers\" href=\"http://developer.android.com/training/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Training - Android Developers</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"API Guides - Android Developers\" href=\"http://developer.android.com/guide/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">API Guides - Android Developers</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Reference - Android Developers\" href=\"http://developer.android.com/reference/packages.html\" target=\"_blank\">Reference - Android Developers</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Design - Android Developers\" href=\"http://developer.android.com/design/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Design - Android Developers</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Performance Tips - Android Developers\" href=\"http://developer.android.com/training/articles/perf-tips.html\" target=\"_blank\">Performance Tips - Android Developers</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"[GUIDE] Best Practices for Android Java\" href=\"http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=2635275\" target=\"_blank\">[GUIDE] Best Practices for Android Java - XDA Developers</a>','Guía de Estilo para Desarrollo en Android','','inherit','open','open','','547-revision-v1','','','2014-03-22 01:52:50','2014-03-22 01:52:50','',547,'http://wiki.4geeks.co/2014/03/547-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(553,16,'2014-03-22 01:54:20','2014-03-22 01:54:20','<address>(Revisión 1.0 - 21/03/2014)</addre